>(水族館) — 3,249 (0.23%)</summary>\n\n| Name | Annual Visitors | Modeled Demand | % of Section |\n|---|---:|---:|---:|\n| 神戸市立須磨海浜水族園 | 1,185,783 | 3,249 | 100.00% |\n\n</details>\n\n## Methodology\n\nResident and commuter totals are derived from employed persons (就業者数) and workers (従業者数) per small census area (小地域), refined by 500m labor mesh and 250m/100m resident mesh to achieve sub-district point placement. Population counts are conserved at the 小地域 level, and point placement is optimized via a mesh-aware loss function.\n\nCommute patterns are modeled using a gravity model augmented by known origin-destination flows at the municipality (市町村) or designated city ward (区) level.\n\n## Data Sources\n\n- 令和2年国勢調査 (2020 National Census) — [e-Stat](https://www.e-stat.go.jp/)\n- 令和3年経済センサス (2021 Economic Census) — [e-Stat](https://www.e-stat.go.jp/)\n- 簡易100mメッシュ人口 (100m Mesh Population) — [GTFS-GIS](https://gtfs-gis.jp/teikyo/)\n- 国土数値情報 (National Land Numerical Information) — [MLIT](https://nlftp.mlit.go.jp/)\n- 空港管理状況調査 (Airport Management Statistics) — [MLIT Aviation](https://www.mlit.go.jp/koku/15_bf_000185.html)\n- 港湾調査 (Port Survey) — [MLIT Ports](https://www.mlit.go.jp/k-toukei/kouwan.html)\n- 大学ポートレート (University Portraits) — [JASSO](https://portraits.niad.ac.jp/)\n- 学校基本調査 (School Basic Survey) — [MEXT](https://www.mext.go.jp/)\n- 観光統計 (Tourism Statistics) — [JNTO](https://statistics.jnto.go.jp/)\n- Overture Maps Foundation — [Overture](https://overturemaps.org/)\n- 海しる / J-EGG500 (Ocean Information / Bathymetry) — [MSIL](https://www.msil.go.jp/) / [JODC](https://www.jodc.go.jp/)\n\n## License\n\nThis map data is released under the [MIT License](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT).\n\n## Attribution\n\nCreated by [ahkimn](https://github.com/ahkimn).",
